abstract: Yehya Sinwar is most senior of Hamas members freed by Israel in exchange for Gilad Shalit, and he returns to Gaza and a world he could not possibly have imagined during his long incarceration.
snippet: Yehya Sinwar is the most senior of the Hamas members freed into Gaza in exchange for Gilad Shalit, and he came home to a world he could not possibly have imagined.
